These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, mirinda, sprite
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, tiparillo, alhambra, pall-mall
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, snowmobile, subway, van
1. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
4. the person drinking cola is the bluemaster-smoker##1
5. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
6. the person driving the bike is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
7. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage    | fanta  | sprite | mirinda    | cola       |
| Cigar         | tiparillo | pall-mall    | alhambra      | bluemaster |
| Transport   | bike   | subway | snowmobile | van        |

