.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, rat, fish, guinea-pig
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, lawyer, musician, social-worker
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, motorbike, roller
1. the person driving the roller is on the left of the social-worker##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the musician is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the person driving the bike is the fisherman##1
6. the person driving the roller is the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Pet        | fish   | rat | hedgehog     | guinea-pig      |
| Job         | lawyer | musician | social-worker | fisherman |
| Transport   | car    | roller   | motorbike     | bike      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, rock-climbing, singing, video-games
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, electronic, hip-hop, pop
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, tram, car, roller
1. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
3. the fan of pop is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is the fan of hip-hop##1
5. the person driving the roller is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
6. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the car##1
7. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | gardening | rock-climbing | singing | video-games |
| Music-Genre   | pop       | electronic    | country | hip-hop     |
| Transport   | boat | car    | roller | tram    |

