There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, mauve, ivory, chestnut
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, car, scooter, tram
1. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the photographer##1
3. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
4. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
5. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the car##1
6. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the videographer##1
7. the person who likes yellow is the person driving the scooter##1
8. the person who likes ivory is the bartender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Job         | bartender  | videographer | photographer  | social-worker |
| Color       | ivory | mauve        | chestnut | yellow       |
| Transport   | airplane   | car          | tram          | scooter       |

