4. the french is on the left of the colombian##1
5. the american is on the right of the fan of metal##1
6. the french is on the left of the fan of blues##1
7. the american is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Hobby         | traveling | chess    | baking        | reading |
