The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, bartender, police-officer, journalist
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, helicopter, motorbike, roller
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the police-officer##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the journalist##1
3. the social-worker is on the left of the person driving the car##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the left of the police-officer##1
5. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
6. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
7. the person watching mystery movies is on the far right##1
8. the bartender is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | drama   | superhero  | comedy    | mystery    |
| Job   | journalist | police-officer  | social-worker  | bartender |
| Transport     | roller  | helicopter | motorbike | car        |

