.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-18::.
There are 4 different nationalities: british, indonesian, mexican, russian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, cycling, rowing, tennis
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, baccarat, dannemann, dunhill
1. the indonesian is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the chaman-smoker is on the far left##1
3. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the british##1
4. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
5. the dannemann-smoker is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
7. the mexican is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Nationality   | british | indonesian | mexican | russian |
| Sport         | cycling | basketball | tennis  | rowing  |
| Cigar     | chaman  | baccarat | dunhill     | dannemann  |

