.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, chess, woodworking, writing
4 different pets are kept: pony, bird, ferret, guinea-pig
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, car, taxi, trike
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
3. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
5. the person driving the car is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
7. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby       | card-games | chess | writing | woodworking |
| Pet         | pony | bird  | guinea-pig   | ferret      |
| Transport   | car        | taxi  | trike   | bus         |

